ygData.msgSnippet: another wind related question.  I think I read that the Charismatic Carrillion is listed as a wind song.  Is there an added effect for using a flute with it
ygData.messageBody:
another wind related question. I think I read that the Charismatic
Carrillion is listed as a wind song. Is there an added effect for using a
flute with it and why am I not dancing?
has it been de-winded?
Penaden
